abstract: On Monday on Nickelodeon, the first-ever made-for-TV “Spongebob” movie, “Atlantis SquarePantis,” attracted a staggering 8.8 million viewers at 8 p.m. The movie, which featured a special voice-over by David Bowie, was Monday night’s No. 1 entertainment program on cable.
